io.elegie.luchess.core.domain.entities

Class Continuation

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.elegie.luchess.core.domain.entities.Continuation

  • public class Continuation
extends java.lang.Object
    A continuation associates some statistics to a given move. It is typically used in a game tree to suggest alternative moves in a given position, and provide some statistics about following variations (i.e. which color tends to win in the given position).
